---------------------------------------------
OKTAEDER.COM - 256b intro by Rudi / DKE
---------------------------------------------
World's first 3dfx Voodoo 1 accelerated 256b?

Features: 
* Bare-metal PCI Voodoo init
* Unreal Mode / 32-bit Flat
* CORDIC 3D rotations
* 8-bit Geometry Lathe
* Lambert shading & 3D Projection

Shows a rotating 3D octahedron.

Requires: DOSBox-X (hardware untested).

Keep the 256b scene alive!
